Package: cellpypes
Title: Cell Type Pipes for Single-Cell RNA Sequencing Data in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Felix",
           family = "Frauhammer",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "felixfrauhammer@gmail.com")
Description: cellpypes implements manual thresholding of marker genes to annotate
    cell types in single-cell RNA sequencing data.
    cellpypes models technical noise to find positive and negative cells for
    a given expression threshold, 
    and the popular piping operator %>% is used to combine rules to complex
    cell type hierarchies.
URL: https://github.com/FelixTheStudent/cellpypes
BugReports: https://github.com/FelixTheStudent/cellpypes/issues
